        android:text="             I also understand that the novel coronavirus, COVID-19, has been declared a worldwide pandemic by the World Health Organization. I further understand that COVID-19 is extremely contagious and is belived to spread by person-to-person contact and accordingly, federal and state health agencies recommend social distancing. \n \n             I recognize that the technicians at Platinum Lashes are closely monitoring this situation and have put in place reasonable preventative measures targeted to reduce the spread of COVID-19. Given the nature of the virus, however, I understand there is an inherent risk ofbecoming infected with COVID-19 by virtue of proceeding with this elective service/treatment. \n \n          Accordingly. I acknowledge and assume the risk of becoming infected with COVID-19 through this elective service/treatment, and I give my express permission for the technicians and staff at Platinum Lashes to proceed with the same. \n \n            I understand that even if I have been tested for COVID-19 and received a negativve test result, the tests in some cases may fail to detect the virus or I may have contracted COVID-19 after the test. I understand that if I have a COVID-19 infection and even if I do not have any symptoms, proceeding with this elective treatment/procedure can lead to a higher chance of complication and death."
